				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=5033&amp;sid=0bd0bb88662b15e95004278d23d1a6b8#5033"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Tue Jan 08, 2002 3:23 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: DAoC Magic system related to EQ</span></td>
				<td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=5033&amp;sid=0bd0bb88662b15e95004278d23d1a6b8"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
